  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Sendable, AutoCloseable
    public class ControllersMultiTester
extends Command
    Simple automated testing for motors. Add the motors with the specified test using the builder methods, then run the command.

      Add a group of motors to test together with the default function (disables braking and sets the motors to full.) Currently uses only BurnoutTester.
